title: "SOUL: Structured Oversight of Unified Lineage"
abstract: "A governance framework for persistent agent identity in Claude Code. SOUL provides rolling knowledge compaction, conscience-based audit loops, human-authored invariants, and hierarchical genome inheritance to address LLM agent memory degradation."
